data.description: Welcome to this charming, brick-constructed home with spacious open bright 4 bedroom 2 bath with no HOA block construction house in a popular Desert Bell Estates. Ton of upgrades include vinyl flooring throughout the house, newer Cabients,  and counter tops. Well sized master bedroom is split with full bathroom, double sinks, walk-in closet. . Extra room that has been converted to office. Private pool,This property is near lots of shopping, restaurants, and hiking trails, plus minutes to the 101 freeway
